 needs\n\nV. AI + Chat System Implementation\n\nDeploy GPT-powered internal bots and assistants\n\nConnect chat interfaces to internal APIs and tools\n\nSupport teams in building task-specific AI agents\n\nVI . Documentation & Team Enablement\n\nDocument everything like your future self depends on it\n\nTrain and support internal users\n\nAnticipate edge cases, prevent misuse, and design with UX in mind\n\nTOOLKIT & STACK\n-\n\nAutomation / Ops: n8n (self-hosted), Make.com, Zapier, Python or JS scripts\n\nData & Workflow: Airtable, Notion, Google Sheets, Supabase, PostgreSQL\n\nCommunication: Webhooks, REST APIs, GraphQL, OAuth, JSON, Regex\n\nInfra / Hosting: Docker, Cloud Run, Firebase, Railway, Vercel, Render\n\nAI & Assistants: OpenAI, LangChain, vector DBs (e.g. Pinecone, Weaviate)\n\nDO YOU RECOGNIZE YOURSELF?\n-\n\nMust Have\n\nYou’ve shipped production-grade automation systems across teams\n\nYou’re fluent with APIs, HTTP requests, and authentication methods\n\nYou’re comfortable self-hosting tools, deploying them, and maintaining them\n\nYou’ve implemented chatbot systems or assistants connected to internal tools\n\nYou love simplifying complex systems for others and scaling your own work\n\nYou’re a rigorous builder who thinks about edge cases, uptime, and error logs\n\nYou enjoy working cross-functionally with non-technical teams and bringing clarity through documentation\n\nYou thrive on autonomy, problem-solving, and always push to make things cleaner, faster, smarter\n\nPersonality\n\nA Relentless Problem-Solver – you don’t stop until it’s done\n\nDetail-Obsessed & Fast – you notice what others don’t, and move quickly\n\nLow Ego, High Growth – feedback fuels you, not fights you\n\nTeam-First – you win together, and fail forward as one\n\nDriven by Wow – you want people to be amazed by your work\n\nLanguage\n\nFrench & English fluency\n\nCurrently, 20% of the team is International, from the cherry blossoms of Japan, the Canadian lakes and to the forest 